name: Fashion Illustration - "Ombre Blue"
description:
This ia an A4 (approx. 8.5" x 11") archival print of the original portrait illustration by Melissa Weatherholtz

Printed using pigment inks on high quality archival paper.

Titled and signed by artist

Does not come with matte/frame
Watermark will not appear on print

Original Fashion Illustration Portrait was done using 
Mixed Media: 
graphite
pastel pencils
panpastel
